cu.explanation_en: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF changed from '192.168.70.132' to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet and unreachable, causing NG-AMF interface routing failures and preventing CU from connecting to AMF.
cu.explanation_zh: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 从 '192.168.70.132' 更改为 '10.0.0.1'，该地址位于不同子网且不可达，导致 NG-AMF 接口路由失败，阻止 CU 连接到 AMF。

du.explanation_en: remote_n_address changed from '127.0.0.5' to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet and unreachable, causing F1 interface routing failures and preventing DU from connecting to CU.
du.explanation_zh: remote_n_address 从 '127.0.0.5' 更改为 '10.0.0.1'，该地址位于不同子网且不可达，导致 F1 接口路由失败，阻止 DU 连接到 CU。
